                    </div>
                    <span>When I ordered this book I was hoping that there would be some information in it that I could pick from it to point me in the right direction on starting a coffee shop.  I got SO MUCH MORE INFORMATION than I could imagine!  Everything you need to know, I mean everything...from learning about coffee, designing your coffee shop, the equipment & supplies you will need, how to give GREAT customer service, how to have the BEST product line, dealing with staff, customers and everything you should consider in your day to day operations. The ideas on marketing were great and gave me other ideas.  I am keeping this book next to my business plan as I plan on refering to each constantly as a guide.  Thank you Tom and Marybeth for taking the time to write such an informative book!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Not Worth the money</div>
